item.title: Will SteveWillDoIt be reinstated on YouTube by Jan 1, 2026?
item.description: YouTuber Stephen Deleonardis (SteveWillDoIt) was banned in 2022 for severe violations involving gambling promotions. Reports suggest potential reinstatement by January 1, 2026. Market resolves YES if channel becomes active.

resolution.rules: Market resolves YES if SteveWillDoIt's official YouTube channel (@SteveWillDoIt) is active, unbanned, and able to upload new content on or before January 1, 2026. Verification requires the channel to be publicly accessible and not showing a ban notice.
